Founded in 2001 in Hong Kong, Milan Station is a specialty store offering the largest assortment of authentic secondhand branded handbags. Milan Station now has 10 shops in Hong Kong, which are strategically placed at Causeway Bay, Central, Tsim Sha Tsui, Mongkok, Shatin, Tsuen Wan and Yuen Long. After launching the first overseas shop in Macau in July 2007, Milan Station set up the Beijing shop which was opened in November. Our group is a company listed on The Stock Exchange of Hong Kong Limited since 2011 with stock code 01150.
